<div class="container" id="about">
  <h3><i>About Sikho Punjabi</i></h3>
  <p>"Sikho Punjabi" literally translates to "Learn Punjabi!". It may also remind you of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sikhism">Sikhism</a>, which is the primary religion in Punjab, India.</p>
  <p>According to <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Punjabi_language">recent estimates</a>, Punjabi is the 10th most spoken language worldwide. Punjabi is the most widely spoken language in Pakistan, and also ranks 5th in Canada, 4th in the United Kingdom, and 3rd in the Indian subcontinent overall.</p>
