    <div class="col s12">
      <h3>Features:</h3>
      <h4>10 free units, and more available to purchase!</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><p>Learn to read and write Gurmukhi and speak basic Punjabi by studying your free lessons.</p></li>
        <li><p>The lessons are organized into easily digestible units.</p></li>
        <li><p>  Observe progress data in the "report card", and quiz yourself as you learn.</p></li>
        <li><p>Want to learn more? Buy additional units that cover a wider range of vocabulary and phrases appropriate for different situations.</p></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
